description: Cosy up with a warming soup full of Mexican spices and flavours. Top it off with tortilla strips for a satisfying crunch.
keywords: Soup,Low saturated fat,High protein,Low salt,Low sugar
name: Speedy chicken and tortilla strip soup Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 420g canned no-added-salt Mexican style three-bean mix, rinsed, drained

recipeInstructions.text: Heat oil in a large saucepan over medium heat. Cook onion, stirring, for 3 minutes or until soft. Add chilli powder and cook for 1 minute or until fragrant.

Add tomatoes, beans, stock and corn, then bring to the boil over high heat. Reduce heat to medium and simmer, uncovered, for 15 minutes or until reduced slightly. Add chicken and cook for 2 minutes or until heated through.
Serve soup topped with tortilla strips, cheese and coriander.
